<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>

    <div style="width:100%; max-width: 750px; margin:auto; margin-top: 0px !important; padding-top:0px !important; font-family: 'Helvetica', san-serif;">
      <img src="https://thinmanager.com/images/email_headers/PartnerRegisterNoticeHeader.jpg" width="100%" alt="Thank you for creating your account" />

      <div style="padding:25px;">
        <h1 align="center" style="margin-bottom:50px;">Your ThinManager Portal&nbsp;Account Has&nbsp;Been&nbsp;Created</h1>
        <p>Dear <%= @user.firstname %>,</p>

        <p>We are so pleased that you have taken the time to create your ThinManager Portal account. Your account is currently under review to verify your partner role. We will send you an e-mail once your partnership role is verified. While that is happening, please feel free to browse any of the content options available to all partner roles.</p>
        

        <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0px;">ThinManager Portal Resources</h3>
        
        <p style="margin-top:5px;">The <%= link_to "ThinManager Portal", "https://partners.thinmanager.com", target: "_blank" %> is a great place to find documentation, presentations, and other partner resources. Content in the ThinManager Portal is presented based on your partnership role, so the items most important to you are readily available. </p>

        
        <p>Thank you again!</p>
        <br />
        <h3>Tom Jordan</h3>
        <p style="margin-top: -20px;">Marketing Lead<br />
        <a href="mailto:tjordan@thinmanager.com">tjordan@thinmanager.com</a></p>
        <br /><br />
      </div>
    </div>
      
  </body>
</html>